#
# Policy: ssh-limit
# Description:
#  Uses nftables meters to limit ssh connection attempts to 10 per second
#  per host

policy ip protocol tcp tcp dport 22 ct state new meter ssh-meter-v4 { ip saddr limit rate 10/minute } accept
policy ip6 nexthdr tcp tcp dport 22 ct state new meter ssh-meter-v6 { ip6 saddr limit rate 10/minute } accept
policy_log tcp dport 22 drop
